					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13284232#post-4650300</guid>
				<title>Re: RULES UPDATE EIGHT: RESUBMITTING CONTAINMENT PROCEDURES</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13284232/exquisite-corpse-contest#post-4650300</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2020 18:07:47 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>A Random Day</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1841781</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You can <em>only</em> resubmit your containment procedures to fix spelling/grammar errors or change the image source. In that case, you can resubmit them to either (<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589652493" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" >A Random Day</a></span> or <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=778357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589652493" alt="ProcyonLotor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=778357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" >ProcyonLotor</a></span>) in a Wikidot PM, with subject line “Exquisite Corpse Entry Resubmission: Reason for resubmission here”.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13284232#post-4647978</guid>
